text: Inka Wasi (Quechua inka Inca, wasi house, "Inca house", hispanicized spelling Incahuasi) is a mountain in the Andes of Peru, about high. It is situated in the Ayacucho Region, Lucanas Province, Cabana District. It lies south of Anqasi and northeast of Misapata. == References == Category:Mountains of Peru Category:Mountains of Ayacucho Region
